        Initializes a new instance of the WebSiteDeleteParameters class with required arguments.
        Parameters:
        deleteEmptyServerFarm - Indicates if the server farm should be deleted. You can delete the server farm if the web site being deleted is the last web site in a server farm.
        deleteMetrics - Indicates if the metrics for the web site should be deleted.
        deleteAllSlots - Indicates if all slots for the web site should be deleted.
